rem Arcade Entrance
rem 8/17/2017

items kiosk machine
items new yen

do Examine Arcade
 [
  print The entrance is open and people come and go. The kiosk is the way the arcade
  print makes money, you have to use it in order to play the games.
 ]

ifflag have mission
 [
  do Enter Arcade
   [
    print It might be fun to watch kids cut their teeth in the arcade, but you don't
    print have the time.
   ]
 |
  do Examine Contact
   [
    print The gentleman is taller than you. He's dressed in a fine Italian suit and
    print wears a fedora, looking rather out of place for being in this part of Ninsei.
    print He watches the crowd dart in and out of the arcade, but keeps an even closer
    print eye on you.
   ]
 ]

ifflag have mission
 [|
  ifflag signal
   [
    do Signal Contact
     [
      print When he glances your way, you shake your right hand holding three fingers out.
      print
      print He nods, then waves you over.
      go Contact
     ]
   |]
 ]
 
do Walk South
 [
  ifflag have mission
   [
    print You leave the arcade heading south, passing a few buildings only to end up at
    print a local record shop.
    go Outside Record Shop
   |
    print Not without talking to your contact first.
   ]
 ]
